// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0622 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 0db554ef-0e64-554e-8cf7-39c0547d362d

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
